summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2015 FORD EDGE. WHILE DRIVING 65 MPH, THE ROCKER PANEL DETACHED FROM THE PASSENGER SIDE OF THE VEHICLE. THE LOCAL DEALER WAS NOT CONTACTED. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT DIAGNOSED OR REPAIRED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOT NOTIFIED OF THE ISSUE. THE VIN WAS UNKNOWN. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 45,451.
